examples.en: The path was overhung with willow trees.
The overhang of the roof cast a shadow on the ground.
examples.ru: Свес крыши отбрасывал на землю тень.

examples.en: The patio was overhung by a canopy.
The hikers sought protection from the weather under an overhang.
examples.ru: Туристы стали искать защиты от непогоды под навесом.
